WEBVTT

00:02.102 --> 00:04.820
"Something dark is growing inside me.

00:05.490 --> 00:07.346
When I watch him with her,

00:07.352 --> 00:09.793
acting like we never existed, I feel it.

00:10.936 --> 00:13.969
That's... the thing that hurts the most.

00:15.139 --> 00:17.587
The fact he's turned me into someone...

00:17.822 --> 00:19.432
I don't recognize.

00:19.769 --> 00:21.891
Someone eaten up by hate."

